<div><head>《關中記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.2">長安地皆黑壤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.3">城今赤如火，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.4">堅如石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.5">父老所傳盡鑿龍首山土為城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.6">又諸臺闕亦爾。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.7">鍾南山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.8">一名中南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.9">言在天中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.10">居之南，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-1a.11">故曰中南。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.2">昆明池曰神靈沼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.3">堯治水訖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.4">停舡此池，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.5">蓋堯已有池，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1692_CHANT_001-2a.6">漢代因特深廣之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
